Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.42,0:00:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.59,0:00:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,At least carry some sedatives with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You barged into my office at the university\Nand hit me until you broke my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As if you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea what I've been through?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.34,0:00:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The university fired me, my wife left me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to pay an arm and a leg in child support...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and on top of that, a student put\Nall my personal information on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And the nightmare all began\Non the day you invaded my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the day that ruined my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.59,0:00:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a social outcast now,\Nand it's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:00:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I care?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:01:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I never wanted to see your face again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that because we're birds of a feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done some research on you devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And apparently your thirst for blood is aroused\Nat the same time as your sex drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in monster mode in my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You act tough, but you're just a pervert, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.13,0:01:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You were turned on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing Tsukasa Taira with her shirt off,\Nwaiting for me to do her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a silent night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eclipse was beginnin'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasaneau setsuna o
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitto eien to shinjikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's darker than black
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Meikyuu no sora
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari o kou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If bite your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoudou ga mushibande yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... Can I... Can I... Who am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Risei o kakikesu libido
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurayami ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ochikitta
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Minikui sugata ni natte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hito no namida kareta nara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi wa boku o dou omou no ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotae o oshiete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Makka na chi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NMakka na chi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizuna o nurashiai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yowasa o wakeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NYowasa o wakeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Futari wa ikite yuku no ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizu o nameatte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sei o teigi shiatte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai o musabotte
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ego Defense
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what triggered the transformation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The memory of Taira's bare skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, don't tell me, it was from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My blood actually turns you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you got a boner?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,From the nosebleed of a dude\Nyou never wanted to see again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta feel sorry for you devils!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like someone's said\Nsomething like that to me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even blood from an old man\Nlike me turns you on, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost feel sorry for you devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,His blood is actually ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I got your mind off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No more signs of you transforming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess you really do only go full-on devil\Nwhen you're lusting after Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I hit a man and he started bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I felt the urge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I hated that man, but I sucked his blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time I punched this crappy professor,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't feel the urge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone you'd do anything to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, you wouldn't understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood is just a minor catalyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing that's triggered my transformation\Nmore than anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Why so calm all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to my eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How is my mind so stable?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on,\Nbut don't be such a wet blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean you're not turned on by my blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabuse, open the door to the next car and wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna use them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When else would I use them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Something more stimulating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Smells good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood dye packs.\NThe Vigilante Corps thought them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's real blood inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,These are valuable prototypes,\Nand you got two of them. You're a lucky man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For a second... I almost had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost found the balance...\Nbetween my mind and my transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, I feel hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm losing the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Did you do her after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you suck her blood while you screwed her?\NIs that how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Maybe she already died in the saddle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I'd known you were going to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have made sure I'd had\Nmy fun with Taira first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, check out those claws!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A devil on the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Close all the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil is in Car 5. Open those doors only!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I wasn't too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, call me into the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently that video was posted by
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the college professor who got a disciplinary\Ndismissal after he tried to assault Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All devil personnel are supposed to be\Nbanned from investigations,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and F Squad's devils in particular are prohibited\Nfrom going outside unchaperoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But now one's gone and wreaked havoc\Non public transportation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and the video of it is all over the internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hand down your punishment later,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but believe me, it will be more than\Nsuspending the one officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And Sawazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were removed from\Nleadership in F Squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Ishimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, this is scary.\NThis can't really be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the devil pests!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,on the Vigilante Corps with\Na personal vendetta against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Internally, I suppose you'll be given\Nthe worst punishment our bylaws allow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, we've taken the position\Nthat you weren't actively deployed;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you just happened to be there\Nand got mixed up in the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if we don't, what you did\Nwas bad enough to easily get you fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher-ups are pretty upset about\Nthat video getting uploaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But even after you transformed,\Nyou didn't hurt the guy. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is a very interesting video.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,See, here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:08:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen his blood and have started\Nto transform, but you're calm and collected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You should take that off. It will get dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As your superior officer, I thought I ought to\Nknow just how much you're capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even their most basic physical abilities\Nfar surpass those of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely there was some opening\Nfor you to hit me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it if you'd actually try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how much control\NI'll have over myself after I transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what I want you to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking? Don't-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just you and me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your girlfriend's not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you do happen to lose control,\NI guarantee I will stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if anyone can do it, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He left a few minutes ago with Ishimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read every file we have on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid of who you are when you transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But on the other hand, you have an\Nintense desire to control your transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I got him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You're faster now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you notice? You have full control over yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that true yesterday, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... in control?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly could not dodge that hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've transformed, but you're thinking rationally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What you are experiencing is what we call\Na benign transformative reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your senses are sharpened,\Nyour reflexes have improved,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can access your maximum muscle strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost 100 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can consciously control what you are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You hadn't realized it yet,\Nbut that is what you're capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be that the sight of human blood is not\Nthe only thing that triggers a transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe your trigger is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You are fast! Can you see my every move?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!\NHow do you know so much about devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you that I'm not your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for the next stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Drinking blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me. I can take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to know more about your potential?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My potential...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Taira!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in full control of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want Tsukasa to see me in devil form.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that guy knows what he's doing\Nwhen it comes to devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been a fan of devils for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a kid,\NI had a playmate who was a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It got me interested,\Nand I started doing research.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what it means\Nto make him transform?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,More or less. I have a basic idea of the extent\Nand method of the transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And how to deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking if you understand how someone\Nwould feel if they were forced to transform?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No good. I can't gain access.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The hideout computer isn't connected to the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't hack in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it always offline?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Maybe they disconnected it to avoid hacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone's thinking that far ahead...\Nit would have to be Zero Two or Zero Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the numbers given in order of importance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two is technically our leader,\Nbut after that, I think it's random.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Number One?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our investor, but I don't know who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who are the other numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why hold back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}01    ? (investor)\N{\an7}02    Zero Two, Kirio Kikuhara\N{\an7}03    X\N{\an7}04    Zero Four, Nakamura\N{\an4}05    Zero Five, Naoya Ushio\N{\an4}06    Zero Six, Takeshi Makimura\N{\an4}07    Zero Seven, Nanako Tenjo\N{\an4}08    X
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4}10     X
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4}09    Zero Nine, Kenichi Yoshii
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}11    Eleven, Sumimori\N{\an8}12    Queen, Kanzaki\N{\an8}13    Jason\N{\an5}14    X\N{\an5}15    Fifteen, Murakami\N{\an5}X = probably no one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these ones marked "probably no one"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen them at the hideout\Nor heard the names,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so I think the numbers got skipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't actually know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eleven, Sumimori\N{\an5}Queen, Kanzaki
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:13:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Jason\NSo one-three (juu-san) isn't Thirteen, it's "Jason"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know there is a Jason, but I don't know their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good. Is there any way to prove\Nthat there's no one in those numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could see the roster, it should tell us\Nwhich numbers haven't been assigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we want to get the roster,\Nwe might have to break into the hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask some other squads for backup,\Nbut we don't know who might be a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Worst case scenario, our squad will go it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean you're over your hatred of devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm putting it on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mad at me? For shooting you\Nand putting a hole in your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That I got shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be apologizing to Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When you shot through that window...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a piece of glass cut her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it doesn't bother me anymore.\NActually, I kind of like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:13:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "hole in his chest"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a-! What are you-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I never heard anything about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, how could an injury like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!\NFirst off, how could an injury like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't have healed that fast!\NThat 7.62mm bullet went right through you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. That was when...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you value your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost everyone here already knows\Nabout Anzai's injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this doesn't leave this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There was once a detective who discovered that devils\Ncould heal their wounds by drinking human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he get fired or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, he was transferred\Nfrom field work, but he was demoted,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the end he quit being a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in the medical world,\Nthe healing properties of blood drinking
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,are treated as top secret information.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't look like he's hearing anything new.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it so secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Because devils might attack someone\Nevery time they get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But we wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The general public doesn't exactly trust devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially devils who have transformed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do? We already know the secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it doesn't leave this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of losing my subordinates\Nover something so unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki, I want a report about this chest wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.51,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Everyone else, take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I had something to give you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Some new equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The manual's in there, so you can try it all out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When I transform, it brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,From when I was a kid.\NThere's a man beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A man you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirio Kikuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A police inspector in Public Security Division 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel like I've said that name before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't have any\Nclear memories of meeting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:16:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that you forgot because it was\Nsuch a terrible memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a type of self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what happened,\Nyou're better off not remembering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't the same as analyzing yourself\Nto get to know yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things are better left not known.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like, if I remember, then I can\Nfigure out something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a basement,\Nwith scary devils everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me I was just like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might find the reason I hate devils\Nsomewhere in those memories of Kikuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you hated devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not blaming you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel hatred or prejudice,\Nthen that's what you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never move forward by pretending\Nthose feelings don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought I told you to know yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always thought devils and humans\Nshould stay separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought that devils are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never remembered\Nwhat made me think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I couldn't get mad at\NZero Seven for hating devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:17:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Diet continued deliberations today\Non laws regarding devil regulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,After the upsurge in public interest, the debate\Nbecame rather heated as both parties-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I hate demons\Nhas something to do with Kikuhara...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And the memory was so terrible that I blocked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What could have possibly happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was just a kid back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe now that I'm grown up,\NI can handle remembering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. You're still awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reading case files.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you? Couldn't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thirsty. I'm going to make\Nsome tea. Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,About what happened on the train...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Don't worry about that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They arrested him on the spot.\NHe won't bother us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't have to feel\Nresponsible for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, about today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,With Ishimaru. I mean...\NI'm sorry for scaring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I was a little startled, but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lee said that Mr. Ishimaru knows a lot about devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So I know that he did what he did to help you, Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But to be honest, I was a little jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is... I want to let you drink my blood, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do anything I can to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've felt that way before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've thought, "Why can't I be the one\Nto give you blood?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Even I think it's childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always so amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you always come out and say\Nexactly what's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's that honesty that's pulled me up,\Nand gotten me this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishimaru told me that my transformation is, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a benign transformative reaction or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Benign?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I transform only from seeing blood,\NI can control my emotions and stay rational.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If what he says is true, then someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can stop living in fear of the devil inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that day comes soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, I'm still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise... I'll never give you my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anything else you want me to do,\Nplease don't hesitate to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wondering what I can do...\Nto help you and all the other devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Something different from what you, Sawazaki,\Nand the police are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A fire has broken out in Taito Ward,\NG Squad's jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe the fire started in\Nthe home of a devils' rights activist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The house is owned by a businessman\Nnamed Souzou Shiraki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not public knowledge, but he's well known\Nfor being an advocate for devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't say for sure at this stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's possible that the anti-devil faction\Nis making an example of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on an investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for a devil serial killer\Nnamed Tamaki Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikuhara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai, I can't let you go alo-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Devil serial killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were suspended from duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I met a long time ago, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We've discussed this.\NIt was at the new staff ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No. More than 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about the devil serial killer, Tamaki Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he have no memory of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home. I can't have rubberneckers\Ndisrupting the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirio Kikuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't remember what happened that day,\Nyou have no right to ask me who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember everything that happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I own it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I want to remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sotto tokete yuku you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Motto ai shiaetara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nani o tsutaerareta no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:22:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai o tsumugenai meguriawase
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dare ka yurushite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.67,0:22:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kegareta sugata ga boku de aru koto o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.42,0:22:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aa doushite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Fureru yubi ga furueteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's story of fight together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dakishimetai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.67,0:22:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizu tsukezu ni mamoritai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Anata dake o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's story of desire forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aragai tsuzukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakiagaru shoudou ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Aa, mata boku wa..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep red dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sotto futari tokete yuku you ni...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jason.
